The anxiety of the mission is
beginning to take its toll.

1031
00:53:42,665 --> 00:53:45,278
I recommend a stronger
sedative during the next

1032
00:53:45,328 --> 00:53:46,737
sleeping phase.

1033
00:53:46,787 --> 00:53:48,127
- All right.

1034
00:53:48,177 --> 00:53:50,344
(beeping)

1035
00:53:52,430 --> 00:53:55,347
(machine swooshes)

1036
00:53:57,358 --> 00:54:01,525
(gentle music)
(muffled chattering)

1037
00:54:14,744 --> 00:54:15,577
Thank you.

1038
00:54:16,431 --> 00:54:18,213
- My name is Alicia.

1039
00:54:18,263 --> 00:54:20,152
Bud, just relax and remember,

1040
00:54:20,202 --> 00:54:21,890
when you feel in fear or in danger,

1041
00:54:21,940 --> 00:54:24,430
just concentrate on something else.

1042
00:54:24,480 --> 00:54:26,847
- Well, thank you, Alicia.

1043
00:54:26,897 --> 00:54:28,566
But why are you telling me this?

1044
00:54:28,616 --> 00:54:30,443
- I can't answer that.

1045
00:54:30,493 --> 00:54:31,649
(chuckles)

1046
00:54:31,699 --> 00:54:33,866
- Maybe McCarthy was right.

1047
00:54:33,916 --> 00:54:36,010
This mission is starting to get to me.

1048
00:54:36,060 --> 00:54:38,629
- Do you really believe that?

1049
00:54:38,679 --> 00:54:39,938
- No.

1050
00:54:39,988 --> 00:54:42,662
No, I've been trained too
damn good to believe that.

1051
00:54:42,712 --> 00:54:44,651
Besides, this is somethin'
that everybody's always

1052
00:54:44,701 --> 00:54:46,242
dreamed about.

1053
00:54:46,292 --> 00:54:48,930
You know, when they first told
me that I had been chosen,

1054
00:54:48,980 --> 00:54:51,693
it took me about a week to
