I stopped melting.

1314
01:07:30,989 --> 01:07:32,535
(dramatic music)

1315
01:07:32,585 --> 01:07:34,835
(sizzling)

1316
01:07:37,837 --> 01:07:38,670
Damn you!

1317
01:07:41,235 --> 01:07:42,960
- You must awaken!

1318
01:07:43,010 --> 01:07:46,347
Wake up, there's no time
to lose, Bud, wake up!

1319
01:07:46,397 --> 01:07:49,639
(beeping)
(machine buzzes)

1320
01:07:49,689 --> 01:07:51,877
- [McCarthy] I'm opening
the airlocks, Bud.

1321
01:07:51,927 --> 01:07:52,924
In just a few minutes,

1322
01:07:52,974 --> 01:07:57,248
you're going to be sucked
out into the vacuum of space.

1323
01:07:57,298 --> 01:07:59,433
You'll be floating forever, Bud.

1324
01:07:59,483 --> 01:08:00,857
Maybe in a thousand years

1325
01:08:00,907 --> 01:08:03,820
they'll find your body and bury it.

1326
01:08:03,870 --> 01:08:08,211
I, of course, will continue
to just do my thing.

1327
01:08:08,261 --> 01:08:10,413
I will complete the mission.

1328
01:08:10,463 --> 01:08:14,630
(rapid beeping)
(tense music)

1329
01:08:17,753 --> 01:08:20,086
- [Computer] A, E, O, U, uh.

1330
01:08:22,056 --> 01:08:23,223
A, E, O, U, I.

1331
01:08:25,342 --> 01:08:26,931
- Feminine, please.

1332
01:08:26,981 --> 01:08:28,980
- [Computer] A, E, O, U, I.

1333
01:08:29,030 --> 01:08:31,571
I believe that this finishes
the reprogramming phase

1334
01:08:31,621 --> 01:08:33,704
of this unit's operation.

1335
01:08:34,633 --> 01:08:38,408
- Yep, well, it's taken a few years.

1336
01:08:38,458 --> 01:08:42,020
But what the hell, I wasn't
goin' any place anyway.

1337
01:08:42,070 --> 01:08:43,309
- [Computer] Yes, Commander.

1338
01:08:43,359 --> 01:08:44,526
- Call me Bud.

1339
01:08:44,576 --> 01:08:46,541
- [Computer] Yes, Bud.

1340
01:08:46,591 --> 01:08:48,689
And what are you going to call me?

1341
01:08:48,739 --> 01:08:50,407
(gentle music)
(beeping)

1342
01:08:50,457 --> 01:08:51,805
- How 'bout Alicia?

1343
01:08:51,855 --> 01:08:53,853
- [Alicia] I like that, Bud.

1344
01:08:53,903 --> 01:08:56,108
Alicia sounds very nice.

1345
01:08:56,158 --> 01:08:58,304
(beeping)

1346
01:08:58,354 --> 01:09:00,937
(gentle music)

1347
01:09:05,878 --> 01:09:09,734
- I don't know, Commander, I
could tell ya it was anxiety.

1348
01:09:09,784 --> 01:09:13,200
I could tell ya many clinical reasons.

1349
01:09:13,250 --> 01:09:17,080
I don't know if there's
anything out there to fear.

1350
01:09:17,130 --> 01:09:18,956
Maybe the only thing we have to fear

1351
01:09:19,006 --> 01:09:21,589
is what we bring along with us.

1352
01:09:22,578 --> 01:09:26,245
(gentle instrumental music)

1353
01:09:45,193 --> 01:09:49,193
(moves into solemn jazzy music)
